From May 8, the following scheduled premises will be allowed to resume operation subject to conditions – 
(a) amusement game centre;
(b) fitness centre;
(c) place of amusement;
(d) place of public entertainment;
(e) beauty parlour;
(f) massage establishment; and
(g) mahjong-tin kau premises; 

Club-house will be allowed to continue operation subject to conditions. 

The following scheduled premises will be required to remain closed – 
(a) bathhouse;
(b) party room;
(c) club or night club; and
(d) karaoke establishment
